{"tid":984913,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]請教防走貓方法","createTime":"2019-01-17T07:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T13:49:55.000Z","uid":34978,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f85ffbc2441f4b973c24bd6c02a568ae72aec93a","tid":984913,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:39:31.000Z","msg":"養貓嘅各位請問大家點樣防走貓<br />\n每日岀入門口都好驚<br />\n佢而家一聽到鎖鑰聲就會衝去門口<br />\n試過幾次一開門嗰陣衝咗岀嚟<br />\n試過跑到去𨋢口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後自己跑返入屋<br />\n好驚佢越跑越遠 或者跑入𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送上貓圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnQfvzC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnQfvzC.png&h=098265f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc7256572b99a0623e4e82c4d2d88d4e8904cdef","tid":984913,"uid":65686,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"要多啲圖先可以幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3770ddf6b089e02adc417239118d6d7d607d566d","tid":984913,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32a58d43ab164eb59b609646c228f26759db5aa5","tid":984913,"uid":16061,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:52:22.000Z","msg":"我兩隻貓開大個門都唔敢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee293d9c58c9393599694d28111f07341f526983","tid":984913,"uid":34978,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSnajxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSnajxD.png&h=d46b412a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5nJEym.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5nJEym.png&h=bfa15380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WkGyhkf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkGyhkf.png&h=48c978ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望唔會相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219c7326f8affe620f251d3569132debb5dcd91b","tid":984913,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:56:30.000Z","msg":"我隻貓岩岩養果時都係咁<br />\n一開門就狗衝出去<br />\n有次一路跑一路另轉頭望我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我老豆整左塊板欄住<br />\n不過煩少少每次出入都要跨過去"},{"pid":"56d5cf56b1f66d9504c79e8fa24d3b11fb93a009","tid":984913,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"我以前養果隻都係自出自入"},{"pid":"065eac3a89b3c0793076e6ea957292162708eaea","tid":984913,"uid":193131,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"開門果時習慣開少少門就用一隻腳檔住，確認左佢位置先真係開門"},{"pid":"74a373671dd7b034f3f62c72247ffca1008b77fd","tid":984913,"uid":40101,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:59:53.000Z","msg":"我果隻都係咁, <br />\n次次我一開門佢就衝出去係門口遊幾個圈, <br />\n捉左幾次之後發現佢原來一聽到我閂門佢就會走返入黎, <br />\n我就開始放棄攔住佢, 由佢係出去行下, 佢八夠就自己返入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c46dd9e39a3cb870b6e029acedec2e6863463e9","tid":984913,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:00:18.000Z","msg":"整多度門喺屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f11382c4fe3952a0d271e561f69bc53b87c0063","tid":984913,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"喵喵喵 喵 喵喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ada69e1e8c8ab71ce39ab580b19631b4e643be2","tid":984913,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56d5cf56b1f66d9504c79e8fa24d3b11fb93a009","tid":984913,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"我以前養果隻都係自出自入"},"citedBy":